        <pre>
<span class="ferrari-red">⭐ 3MTPS GOLD LOAN SERVICE — COMPLETE MASTER RULEBOOK</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">3MTPS Pvt Ltd – Money Makes Many Things Public Service Pvt Ltd</span>

<span class="barbie-pink">“Public Health and Wealth are Our Greatest Happiness”</span>

<span class="hermes-orange">Introduction: Why 3MTPS Gold Loans Exist</span>
<span class="matrix-green">In India, people often depend on gold loans for emergency support—medical needs, family duties, education fees, house repairs, business capital, or unexpected expenses. But the biggest problem is that most loan systems work against the customer, not for them. High interest rates, hidden charges, harassment, and uncertain gold safety have caused fear and mistrust.</span>

<span class="rolex-gold">3MTPS was created to solve these problems permanently.</span>

<span class="lamborghini-yellow">3MTPS Gold Loan Service is designed with one powerful belief</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">“Money Makes Many Things — But Public Service Makes Life Beautiful.”</span>

<span class="neon-cyan">Our gold loan model protects:</span>
<span class="pink">Poor people</span>
<span class="yellow">Middle-class families</span>
<span class="matrix-green">Farmers</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">Widows</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">Students</span>
<span class="ferrari-red">Daily wage workers</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">Small business owners</span>
<span class="barbie-pink">Anyone who suddenly needs financial help</span>

<span class="rainbow-text">At the same time, the company must be protected from people who try to cheat, because:</span>
<span class="matrix-green">If a few people cheat the company, the entire service will collapse, and thousands of families will lose support.</span>

<span class="hermes-orange">So, our system is built with:</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">Strict rules</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">Clear communication</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">Zero corruption</span>
<span class="pink">Zero leniency for cheaters</span>
<span class="yellow">Complete support for genuine customers</span>

<span class="ferrari-red">This is the heart of the 3MTPS Gold Loan sector.</span>

<span class="rolex-gold">Our Mission</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">The mission of 3MTPS:</span>
<span class="matrix-green">To give low-interest, honest gold loans</span>
<span class="barbie-pink">To maintain gold safety like family treasure</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">To help society with transparent rules</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">To prevent customers from falling into debt traps</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">To save families from financial stress</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">To ensure the company grows responsibly without risk</span>

<span class="pink">We are not competitors to banks or private financiers.</span>
<span class="yellow">We are a Public Service Pvt Ltd — created to serve society with humanity and responsibility.</span>

<span class="ferrari-red">Customer Responsibilities</span>
<span class="matrix-green">3MTPS is ready to support every genuine customer, but customers also have responsibilities:</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">Provide genuine gold</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">Use real documents</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">Pay interest on time</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">Respond to calls/messages</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">Maintain good communication</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">Follow our rules strictly</span>

<span class="pink">If customers fail to communicate or attempt cheating, the company must take action for safety.</span>

<span class="yellow">How We Check Gold (100% Genuine Method)</span>
<span class="matrix-green">3MTPS follows a multi-level gold verification process to ensure purity and fairness.</span>

<span class="ferrari-red">A. Manual Verification</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">Visual inspection</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">Magnet test</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">Surface checking</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">Sound test</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">Density test</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">Scratch & streak test on testing stone</span>
<span class="pink">Comparison with BIS standards</span>

<span class="yellow">These methods give a first-level assessment.</span>

<span class="ferrari-red">B. Digital Verification</span>
<span class="matrix-green">We use modern machines:</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">Karat analyzer</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">Laser gold purity machine</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">Digital weighing scales (0.01 accuracy)</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">XRF testing machine</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">Microscopic inspection</span>

<span class="pink">This ensures exact purity.</span>

<span class="yellow">C. Final Gold Approval</span>
<span class="matrix-green">If gold purity is 100% guaranteed, then loan value is calculated.</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">If gold is low purity (18K / 20K / 22K), loan amount reduces based on purity.</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">We never give full market value.</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">We give only 60% maximum loan-to-value (LTV).</span>

<span class="ferrari-red">Example: Gold Calculation (100% Purity)</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">If 10 grams gold value = ₹1,00,000</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">3MTPS gives only ₹50,000 to ₹60,000 (max)</span>

<span class="pink">This protects both customer and company.</span>

<span class="yellow">5. Loan Value Rules</span>
<span class="matrix-green">We calculate loan amount based on:</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">Purity</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">Weight</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">Market rate</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">60% LTV limit</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">Customer history</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">Documentation</span>

<span class="pink">We never give 90% or 100% value because it risks the company and encourages cheating.</span>

<span class="ferrari-red">Interest Structure (Very Clear & Strict)</span>
<span class="matrix-green">A. Monthly Payment Plan (Normal Scheme)</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">₹1 interest per ₹100 per month</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">Example:</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">Loan: ₹50,000</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">Monthly Interest: ₹500</span>

<span class="matrix-green">B. Delayed or Long-Term Plan (If customer doesn’t pay monthly)</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">₹1.50 per ₹100 per month</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">Example:</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">Loan: ₹50,000</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">Monthly Interest: ₹750</span>

<span class="pink">This applies when customers pay interest once in 3, 6, or 12 months.</span>

