<span class="ferrari-red">4. What Is Wrong with Market Oils Today?</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">To understand why 3MTPS oils are important, you need to know how normal market oils are produced:</span>

<span class="pink">A. 1: Chemical Refining</span>
<span class="yellow">Most factory oils are refined using:</span>
<span class="matrix-green">Sodium hydroxide</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">Bleaching chemicals</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">Deodorizing chemicals</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">Heat up to 240°C</span>

<span class="lamborghini-yellow">At that temperature, the oil becomes:</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">Dead</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">Toxic</span>
<span class="pink">Harmful to arteries</span>
<span class="yellow">Dangerous for heart</span>
<span class="matrix-green">Cancer-causing</span>

<span class="rolex-gold">B. 2: Blending with cheap oils</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">Many factories mix:</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">Palm oil</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">Cottonseed oil</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">Rice bran oil</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">Artificial flavors</span>

<span class="pink">This is done to reduce cost and increase profit.</span>
<span class="yellow">People eat these oils daily and suffer lifelong health issues.</span>

<span class="matrix-green">C. 3: Repeated Heating</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">Hotels and restaurants heat oils many times.</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">Some factories do the same to reuse leftover oil.</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">This creates trans fats — the biggest reason for:</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">Heart attacks</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">Liver failure</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">Severe inflammation</span>

<span class="pink">D. 4: Plastic Containers</span>
<span class="yellow">Chemicals from plastic enter oil.</span>
<span class="matrix-green">This affects:</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">Hormones</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">Fertility</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">Immune system</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">Child growth</span>

