<span class="lamborghini-yellow">2. INSIDE THE 3MTPS OIL EXTRACTION UNIT</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">3MTPS operates a traditional + scientific hybrid oil extraction model:</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">No chemicals</span>
<span class="pink">No heat</span>
<span class="yellow">No preservatives</span>
<span class="matrix-green">No bleaching</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">No refining</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">No colour adding</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">No fragrance adding</span>

<span class="lamborghini-yellow">We produce 100% wood-pressed, cold-pressed oils with traditional values.</span>

<span class="neon-cyan">⭐ PROCESS STEP–BY–STEP</span>

<span class="chanel-purple">⭐ Step 1: Sun Drying (Natural Moisture Removal)</span>
<span class="pink">All nuts and seeds are dried naturally under sunlight.</span>
<span class="yellow">Sun drying benefits:</span>
<span class="matrix-green">✔ Removes excess moisture</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">✔ Improves oil percentage</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">✔ Kills bacteria and fungus</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">✔ Preserves nutrients</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">✔ Improves seed fragrance</span>

<span class="neon-cyan">We never use heaters or mechanical dryers.</span>

<span class="chanel-purple">⭐ Step 2: Cleaning & Sorting</span>
<span class="pink">We remove:</span>
<span class="yellow">Sticks</span>
<span class="matrix-green">Stones</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">Dust</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">Sand</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">Shell pieces</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">Blackened seeds</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">Infected seeds</span>

<span class="chanel-purple">This step is very important for pure, clean oil.</span>

<span class="pink">⭐ Step 3: Cold-Pressing in Wooden Ghani</span>
<span class="yellow">3MTPS uses the ancient wooden press system.</span>
<span class="matrix-green">Why wooden press?</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">Because metal or steel machines create heat and destroy nutrients.</span>

<span class="tiffany-blue">Wood-pressed extraction:</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">Rotates slowly (40–50 rpm)</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">Generates almost zero heat</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">Preserves natural vitamins</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">Keeps Omega-3, 6, 9 healthy</span>
<span class="pink">Retains aroma</span>
<span class="yellow">Retains color</span>
<span class="matrix-green">Keeps antioxidants safe</span>

<span class="rolex-gold">This is what makes 3MTPS oils taste like grandmother’s oils.</span>

<span class="tiffany-blue">⭐ Step 4: Natural Settling (24 to 48 Hours)</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">After extraction, the oil is kept in stainless steel tanks.</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">During this time:</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">✔ Heavy particles settle at bottom</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">✔ Oil becomes naturally clear</span>
<span class="pink">✔ No need for chemical filtration</span>
<span class="yellow">✔ No whitening or refining needed</span>

<span class="matrix-green">This method gives pure clarity and long shelf life.</span>

<span class="rolex-gold">⭐ Step 5: Cotton Cloth Filtration</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">We use:</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">Multi-layer cotton cloth</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">Micro filters</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">Gravity filtering</span>

<span class="chanel-purple">No machines are used that heat oil.</span>

<span class="pink">Benefits:</span>
<span class="yellow">✔ Zero chemical contact</span>
<span class="matrix-green">✔ Pure aroma maintained</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">✔ Pure texture</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">✔ Pure nutrients preserved</span>

<span class="hermes-orange">⭐ Step 6: Zero-Plastic Storage</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">3MTPS never stores oil in plastic tanks.</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">Food-grade steel</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">Glass containers</span>
<span class="pink">Metal storage drums</span>

<span class="yellow">Plastic destroys nutrition.</span>
<span class="matrix-green">Plastic releases micro-toxins.</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">Plastic spoils aroma.</span>

<span class="tiffany-blue">3MTPS ensures 100% safe storage.</span>

