<span class="neon-cyan">📘 PART 3 – ORGANIZATIONAL STRUCTURE & MANAGEMENT SYSTEM</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">3MTPS operates through a well-planned organizational structure designed to maintain quality, systematic operations, and smooth delivery across all 21 services. Since the company handles multiple sectors—food, agriculture, education, technology, financial services, transport, entertainment, and social welfare—our management system ensures professional coordination in every activity.</span>

<span class="pink">1. ORGANIZATIONAL MODEL</span>
<span class="yellow">3MTPS follows a Centralized Strategy + Decentralized Execution model:</span>
<span class="matrix-green">Centralized Strategy:</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">All decisions related to policies, service standards, quality levels, pricing, procurement rules, and customer policies are taken by the central management.</span>

<span class="tiffany-blue">Decentralized Execution:</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">Each service operates with a dedicated team that handles daily operations, field activities, customer service, logistics, and quality verification.</span>

<span class="lamborghini-yellow">This combination allows the company to maintain consistent standards while handling large-scale operations efficiently.</span>

<span class="neon-cyan">2. DIRECTOR BOARD & EXECUTIVE MANAGEMENT</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">A. Board of Directors</span>
