<span class="neon-cyan">📘 PART 4 – QUALITY STANDARDS, CERTIFICATIONS & BRAND STRENGTH</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">3MTPS maintains strict quality frameworks to ensure trust, purity, and safety. These standards help us deliver services that match or exceed expectations.</span>

<span class="pink">1. QUALITY STANDARDS WE FOLLOW</span>
<span class="yellow">3MTPS follows a 7-Layer Quality Framework across all services:</span>
<span class="matrix-green">1. Direct Source Validation</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">We confirm the original source—farm, mill, factory, fishing area, or supplier.</span>

<span class="tiffany-blue">2. Purity Check</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">We test for chemicals, adulteration, mixing, and contamination.</span>

<span class="lamborghini-yellow">3. Nutritional Value Testing</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">Especially for fruits, vegetables, dry fish, millets, water, and animal feed.</span>

<span class="chanel-purple">4. Hygiene & Cleaning Protocols</span>
<span class="pink">Drying, washing, cutting, packing—all follow strict hygiene rules.</span>

<span class="yellow">5. Storage Control</span>
<span class="matrix-green">Temperature, moisture, and cleanliness are monitored daily.</span>

<span class="rolex-gold">6. Secure Packing</span>
<span class="tiffany-blue">We use tamper-proof, durable, and moisture-resistant packaging.</span>

<span class="hermes-orange">7. Final Inspection</span>
<span class="lamborghini-yellow">Every product batch is approved before release.</span>

<span class="neon-cyan">2. CERTIFICATIONS (Depending on Service Category)</span>
<span class="chanel-purple">3MTPS maintains or targets certifications under these categories:</span>
<span class="pink">• FSSAI – Food Safety Standards</span>
<span class="yellow">For edible oils, dry fruits, spices, millets, fruits, vegetables, dry fish, animal feed (as applicable).</span>

<span class="matrix-green">• ISI Standards</span>
<span class="rolex-gold">For packaging, manufacturing, water cans, bags, and notebooks.</span>

<span class="tiffany-blue">• Mineral Testing Reports</span>
<span class="hermes-orange">For 3MTPS water (calcium, magnesium, chloride values etc.)</span>

<span class="lamborghini-yellow">• Hygiene & Safety Compliance</span>
<span class="neon-cyan">Workplace sanitation and food handling certifications.</span>

<span class="chanel-purple">• Technology Compliance</span>
<span class="pink">Cyber security, data protection, and AI-based verification standards for the Online Voting System.</span>

<span class="yellow">• Financial Compliance</span>
<span class="matrix-green">For gold loans, Family Care Fund, and company accounts.</span>

